binaryTree
Interface BinaryTreeNode<T>

All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultBinaryTreeNode
public interface BinaryTreeNode<T>

BinaryTreeNode is the interface for a basic binary tree node, with data of type T and pointers to left and right children.
